dcterms:description: Sentinel-1 is a C-band SAR satellite system launched by ESA, whose missions include sea and land monitoring, emergency response after environmental disasters, and commercial applications.
dcterms:title: Sentinel-1

dcterms:description: TerraSAR-X is an X-band Earth observation SAR satellite operated under a public-private partnership between the German Aerospace Center (DLR) and EADS Astrium, known for its high resolution and excellent geometrical accuracy.
dcterms:title: TerraSAR-X
